<div class="guide-section">
  <h3>This Week</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Audit all models your org uses. Check <a href="https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/deprecations">OpenAI's deprecation docs</a>, <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/">Anthropic</a>, and other providers for announced EOLs.</li>
    <li>Create a deprecation register (spreadsheet or GitHub issues).</li>
